之精。精之案為眼，骨之精為瞳子；筋之精為黑眼，血之精為力絡。其案氣之精為白眼，肌肉之精為約束。裹擷筋骨血氣之精，而與脈並為系。"},{"pid":"3aef3cc084cc3025506c37972d59b3e9b56bef4f","tid":1136583,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:59:48.000Z","msg":"試咩玄學都好 唔好試中藥就得"},{"pid":"a37d17445d56348914f039febb65426731057952","tid":1136583,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55ab9b45a41cf774e2160cc3bd0cbbd15cb13543","tid":1136583,"uid":122139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:43:08.000Z","msg":"切左佢得唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"開咗大刀 醫生望咗兩望 縫返埋"},{"pid":"de750a2f163e470fcfe15da7f9124cd144c5a80a","tid":1136583,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c391ef660553f9309b6a888ac7fdb43af3013e65","tid":1136583,"uid":59526,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾信唔D偽科學<br />\n去黃大仙飲符水死左佢好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"走投無路都唔介意咩都試下"},{"pid":"ed8c745285a0823d3f042cbd80be47c7e793e195","tid":1136583,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68698e0dc5eb6b9c66e9f6f09f61ebe5cb0c9d93","tid":1136583,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:57:32.000Z","msg":"胰臟癌第幾期？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:33:20.000Z","msg":"末期"},{"pid":"ad5a22eab4e0ce18d151dd519d58cb6833484b5d","tid":1136583,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0571b23730ce2886e1a2c61e8b50af554b2cdae","tid":1136583,"uid":171520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"查下有無冤親債主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"都有"},{"pid":"6401988f4d26ff787abbf1de0c21e5b1e62d38fc","tid":1136583,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f007cfd2f51be4040e6b3ec27989053731b2da54","tid":1136583,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:14:44.000Z","msg":"睇黎你老豆好多身家<